An implementation of the model object 'Content Element'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Variability Type
  • Variability Based On Element
  • Supporting Materials
  • Concepts And Papers
  • Checklists
  • Guidelines
  • Examples
  • Assets
  • Termdefinition
